singersongwriter sergio franchi died 
tuesday at his estate here after a prolonged battle with cancer 
his family said 
although the italian native never publicly revealed his age 
records showed that he was 57 
franchi a oncefrequent guest of the ed sullivan show 
performed at concerts around country and was a regular on the las 
vegas club circuit 
he made 25 albums and was known for such hits as o solo 
mio wind beneath my wings and memory 
franchi performed in concert last year in china 
he is survived by his wife eva a daughter greta a son 
roberto two sisters and two grandchildren his brotherinlaw 
peter catalano announced the death tuesday in new york 
