american hostages and the others from other countries held against 
their will things seem to be moving on this 
and mr polhill welcome to the white house and i just cant 
tell you how overjoyed barbara and i are to have both of you here 
mr polhill thanks very much president bush i feel very badly 
that i cant talk to you quite as well as id like to be able to 
