born on the fourth of july and foxs nightbreed nearly tied 
for fifth place with born winning on the final tally both 
studios insisted the numbers were fair and cried trickery 
explained one studio executive anybody in this end of the 
business can go down those numbers and tell you whos exaggerating 
and whos not and by how much theyre exaggerating 
