broadcasting system headquarters where 2400 police staged a 
midnight raid monday to end a 19day protest against the networks 
new president police arrested 333 workers 
workers at the nations only other network the munwha 
broadcasting co began a fiveday sympathy strike on tuesday 
virtually crippling the nations broadcasting industry 
programming was curtailed at the three networks five stations 
and 19 local stations run by the two companies 
