cashed all his checks and left a note for the milkman telling him 
he wouldnt be needed for a while 
then he shot his wife over breakfast his mother in her bed when 
she asked what the noise was and then each child as they came home 
from school 
he left a note for his pastor and fled taking on the alias 
robert p clark an accountant first in metropolitan denver and 
then near richmond va 
he remarried and again became active in his church his second 
wife delores clark has remained out of the public spotlight since 
his arrest 
list was arrested on a tip generated after the television 
anticrime show americas most wanted reenacted the slayings 
</TEXT>
