in addition gets more than 600 million in other side benefits 
dole asked whether israel should get a break on fees for the 
loan guarantees which would save the israeli government an 
estimated 25 million or more over the 30year life of the loans 
whether requirements for eligibility for the housing should be 
waived as proposed in the bill and whether the money also would 
be used to build roads and parks and pay consultants 
