<TEXT>
eastern europe ignored violenceelsewhere 
and quietly celebrated its freedom from decades of stagnant 
communist ritual on may day substituting music fests and picnics 
for the proletarian parades of the past 
turbulence marked may day demonstrations in south korea west 
berlin mexico turkey and the philippines however 
and in moscow a brief burst of the popular rage that has swept 
