historically sound 
after viewing the results ratner himself took the bold measures 
he called for structuring the health responsibility program and 
its unique point system into a package that can be utilized in any 
companys flexible benefits system 
working with robert thurston of the human resource consulting 
group a salt lake city marketing operation points from ratners 
program can be committed in myriad ways to customized health 
benefit packages offered by employers 
what will the points buy you name it good health to be sure 
but dollars too or more vacation time or lower insurance 
deductibles for example in fact a catalog of possibilities 
already has been developed 
ratner father of two sees the incentives as a way to promote 
not just worker health but that of entire families since family 
members often affect health insurance costs as much or more than 
workers themselves 
americas job he says is to refocus the entire american 
psyche to become aggressive against the enemy of rising costs 
and to beat them he wonders he says how we have remained so 
passive in view of the threat 
