the justice department has said in the past they dont believe 
it is the best use of scant prosecutorial resources to run these 
things down 
lukens comments came after a hearing at which he accused the 
networks of colluding with the cigarette industry to skirt the law 
capital citiesabc and rjr nabisco makers of winston salem 
and camel cigarettes jointly own espn cable television he said 
loews which owns all of lorillard tobacco makers of kent 
newport and true also owns about 25 percent of cbs 
